{
  "info": {
    "name": "Attendance Management API",
    "description": "REST API and WebSocket server for managing classroom attendance.\n\n## WebSocket Testing\n\nConnect to: `ws://localhost:3000/ws?token=<JWT_TOKEN>`\n\n### Events (JSON format):\n\n**ATTENDANCE_MARKED** (Teacher → Broadcast):\n```json\n{\"event\": \"ATTENDANCE_MARKED\", \"data\": {\"studentId\": \"s100\", \"status\": \"present\"}}\n```\n\n**TODAY_SUMMARY** (Teacher → Broadcast):\n```json\n{\"event\": \"TODAY_SUMMARY\"}\n```\n\n**MY_ATTENDANCE** (Student → Unicast):\n```json\n{\"event\": \"MY_ATTENDANCE\"}\n```\n\n**DONE** (Teacher → Persist & Broadcast):\n```json\n{\"event\": \"DONE\"}\n```",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "classId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "studentId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Signup - Teacher",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"John Teacher\",\n  \"email\": \"teacher@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"role\": \"teacher\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/signup",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "signup"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Signup - Student",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Rahul Student\",\n  \"email\": \"student@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"role\": \"student\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/signup",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "signup"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (jsonData.success && jsonData.data.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"token\", jsonData.data.token);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"teacher@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Current User",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "{{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/me",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "me"]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Classes",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create Class",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (jsonData.success && jsonData.data._id) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"classId\", jsonData.data._id);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "{{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"className\": \"Maths 101\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/class",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["class"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Class by ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "{{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/class/{{classId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["class", "{{classId}}"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Add Student to Class",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "{{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"studentId\": \"{{studentId}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/class/{{classId}}/add-student",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["class", "{{classId}}", "add-student"]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Students",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get All Students",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (jsonData.success && jsonData.data.length > 0) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"studentId\", jsonData.data[0]._id);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "{{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/students",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["students"]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Attendance",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Start Attendance Session",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "{{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"classId\": \"{{classId}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/attendance/start",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["attendance", "start"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get My Attendance",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "{{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/class/{{classId}}/my-attendance",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["class", "{{classId}}", "my-attendance"]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
